src: function check({driver_license, udi, period_end, time_zone, zone, payment, guarantee, currency, subvention}) { return driver_license === 'lic2' && udi === 'udi2' && period_end.getTime() === 1547042400000 && time_zone === 'Europe/Moscow' && payment === 500.500 && guarantee === 100.100 && currency === 'RUB' && subvention.amount === 837.3953 && subvention.currency === 'RUB'; }
